text: Gitanas Nausėda (born 19 May 1964) is a Lithuanian politician and economist. He is the 9th and current President of Lithuania since July 2019. He is an Independent politician, which means that he is not associated with any political party. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Economists Category:Presidents of Lithuania Category:Current national leaders Category:Politicians from Vilnius
title: Gitanas Nausėda
